<item>
            <title>[MJAVADOC-55] offline links not generated when offline</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MJAVADOC-55</link>
                <project id="12317529" key="MJAVADOC">Maven Javadoc Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The javadoc plugin (beta-3) in offline mode doesn&apos;t take into account the offlineLinks parameter.&lt;br/&gt;
In JavadocReport.java, line 829:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;if ( !isOffline )&lt;br/&gt;
{&lt;br/&gt;
    addLinkArguments( arguments );&lt;br/&gt;
    addLinkofflineArguments( arguments );&lt;br/&gt;
    ...&lt;br/&gt;
}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Shouldn&apos;t addLinkofflineArguments be outside the if block ?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
